  "body": "### Description\n\n*Type*: Bug\n*Summary*: if you enter wrong word while checking your recovery phrase, in order to continue you need to go back to \"Your recovery phrase\" screen, because word number is overlapped with \"Wrong word\" validation message \n\n#### Expected behavior\nCan see which word is needed \n\n#### Actual behavior\n![Monosnap 2019-04-03 18-02-35](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/55494244-b1a54100-563a-11e9-9e7d-ea19b6bd7401.png)\n\n\n### Reproduction\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n- Open Status\n- Tap on create account -> Keycard -> follow instructions\n- After \"Your recovery phrase\" tap Next\n- Enter wrong word\n\n\n### Additional Information\n\n* Status version: 0.12.0 apk  http://status-im-prs.ams3.digitaloceanspaces.com/StatusIm-190402-123212-80ef5d-pr.apk\n* Operating System: Android 8, LG V20",
